<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="h-100">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>YM-TRANSIT ERP — Portail Intégré de Smart Transit & Douane</title>
  
  <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.2/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- Fonts -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.94) 30%, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88) 100%), url('/assets/ym_transit.jpg') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    h1, h2, h3, h4, .font-display {
      font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    }
    .text-primary-custom {
      color: #38bdf8 !important;
    }
    .bg-primary-custom {
      background-color: #38bdf8 !important;
    }
    .btn-primary-custom {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38bdf8 0%, #0284c7 100%);
      border: none;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-primary-custom:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0369a1 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-outline-custom {
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: #f1f5f9;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .btn-outline-custom:hover {
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .glass-card {
      background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.6);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      border-radius: 16px;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }
    .glass-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }
    .feature-icon-wrapper {
      width: 54px;
      height: 54px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .glass-card:hover .feature-icon-wrapper {
      background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }
    .hero-glow {
      position: absolute;
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56,189,248,0.08) 0%, rgba(56,189,248,0) 70%);
      top: 10%;
      left: 10%;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-glow-right {
      position: absolute;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(2,132,199,0.06) 0%, rgba(2,132,199,0) 70%);
      bottom: 10%;
      right: 5%;
      z-index: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="d-flex flex-column min-vh-100 position-relative overflow-x-hidden">

  <!-- Glows Background -->
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="hero-glow-right"></div>

  <!-- Header / Navbar -->
  <header class="py-4 position-relative" style="z-index: 10;">
    <div class="container d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
        <div class="px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded-3 fw-bold bg-primary-custom text-dark font-display" style="font-size: 1.15rem; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          YM
        </div>
        <div class="font-display fw-bold text-white fs-5 tracking-tight">
          TRANSIT <span class="fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">ERP</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <% if (session && session.userId) { %>
          <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-outline-custom rounded-pill px-4 btn-sm">
            <i class="bi bi-grid-fill me-1.5 text-primary-custom"></i> Tableau de bord
          </a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary-custom rounded-pill px-4 btn-sm">
            <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right me-1.5"></i> Connexion
          </a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <main class="flex-grow-1 d-flex align-items-center py-5 position-relative" style="z-index: 10;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
        <div class="col-lg-6 text-start">
          <span class="badge bg-white bg-opacity-10 text-primary-custom px-3 py-2 rounded-pill font-display text-uppercase mb-3" style="font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
            💡 Smart Transit & Logistique Douanière
          </span>
          <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white tracking-tight lh-sm mb-3">
            Gérez vos opérations de transit avec une précision absolue.
          </h1>
          <p class="lead text-slate-300 mb-4" style="font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            De la déclaration GUCE au suivi CAMCIS, de la validation collégiale des bons provisoires de décaissement jusqu’à la comptabilisation en caisse. Un ERP complet, fluide et sécurisé pour l'excellence de votre fret.
          </p>
          <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <% if (session && session.userId) { %>
              <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-primary-custom btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 py-2.5 shadow">
                Continuer vers l'ERP <i class="bi bi-arrow-right-short ms-1.5"></i>
              </a>
            <% } else { %>
              <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary-custom btn-lg rounded-pill px-5 py-2.5 shadow">
                Accéder au Portail <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill ms-1.5" style="font-size: 0.95rem;"></i>
              </a>
            <% } %>
            <a href="#fonctionnalites" class="btn btn-outline-custom btn-lg rounded-pill px-4 py-2.5">
              Découvrir les Modules
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <!-- Square Cover Image -->
          <div class="glass-card p-0 overflow-hidden mb-4 border-0 shadow-lg" style="border-radius: 16px;">
            <img src="/assets/ym_transit.jpg" alt="YM Transit Logo" class="img-fluid w-100" style="object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 4/3; opacity: 0.9;">
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-4 text-start border-start border-3 border-info">
            <h4 class="fw-bold text-white mb-3">
              <i class="bi bi-activity text-primary-custom me-2"></i>Résumé de la plateforme
            </h4>
            <p class="text-slate-300 small mb-4" style="line-height: 1.55;">
              La plateforme coordonne tous les rôles opérationnels et d'administration sous un cadre de gouvernance strict :
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                <i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-primary-custom mt-1.5" style="font-size: 0.5rem;"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white d-block small">Services de Transit Opérationnels</strong>
                  <span class="text-muted d-block" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Facturation, Douane GUCE, Enlèvement et Livraison, Acconage et Clôture.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                <i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-success mt-1.5" style="font-size: 0.5rem;"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white d-block small">Validation Multi-Visas des Bons</strong>
                  <span class="text-muted d-block" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Visas collégiaux obligatoires (PDG, DG, DGA, DAF, Audit) pour les décaissements.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3">
                <i class="bi bi-circle-fill text-warning mt-1.5" style="font-size: 0.5rem;"></i>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white d-block small">Suivi Collaboratif par Tâches</strong>
                  <span class="text-muted d-block" style="font-size: 0.8rem;">Tableau Kanban, notifications en temps réel pour l'acteur concerné et rapports d'activité.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="border-top border-secondary border-opacity-30 pt-4 mt-4 text-center">
              <span class="text-xs text-muted font-monospace text-uppercase" style="font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
                ✨ Intégrité • Rapidité • Traçabilité
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Section Fonctionnalités -->
  <section id="fonctionnalites" class="py-5 bg-black bg-opacity-20 position-relative" style="z-index: 10;">
    <div class="container py-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-5">
        <span class="text-xs fw-bold text-primary-custom tracking-wider font-monospace text-uppercase mb-2 d-block">
          Architecture Évoluée
        </span>
        <h2 class="h1 fw-bold text-white mb-3">Une Plateforme, Zéro Compromis</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400 small">Une suite d’outils intégrés répondant aux besoins de l'ensemble de vos équipes de fret.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="row g-4">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100 text-start">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrapper mb-3">
              <i class="bi bi-folder2-open text-primary-custom fs-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-white">Dossiers de Transit</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 small mb-0" style="line-height: 1.55;">
              Centralisation complète de vos dossiers d'import et d'export. Suivi de statut, attachement de documents administratifs et de factures fournisseurs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100 text-start">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrapper mb-3">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-fill-check text-primary-custom fs-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-white">Circuit de Visas Sécurisé</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 small mb-0" style="line-height: 1.55;">
              Les Bons Provisoires exigent le visa électronique obligatoire de chaque décideur (PDG, DG, DGA, DAF, Audit). Aucune erreur ou oubli n'est toléré.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="glass-card p-4 h-100 text-start">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrapper mb-3">
              <i class="bi bi-kanban-fill text-primary-custom fs-4"></i>
            </div>
            <h5 class="fw-bold text-white">Bureau Kanban & Tâches</h5>
            <p class="text-slate-400 small mb-0" style="line-height: 1.55;">
              Assignez des étapes, suivez la progression par glisser-déposer interactif, échangez des consignes et recevez des alertes instantanées.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-4 border-top border-secondary border-opacity-10 position-relative" style="z-index: 10; background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="text-muted mb-0 small">&copy; 2026 YM-TRANSIT ERP — Tous droits réservés.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
